{"type":"message","id":"d8921dfd","parentId":"0835f0c4","timestamp":"2026-04-14T10:40:17.042Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4dr5v599lytd_1","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"07cdf349780f84851f44e5ab68761cdbe5f6e4a62559b8fbf3f07e739935bf41\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/dtlx-context.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 1,\n      \"endLine\": 46,\n      \"score\": 0.7405801153101165,\n      \"textScore\": 0.7405801153101165,\n      \"snippet\": \"# AHV DTLX Project Context\\n\\n_Last updated: 2026-04-12 by Orbis_\\n\\n## ⚠️ CRITICAL — System Architecture\\n\\n**DTLX và QLHV là 2 hệ thống DÙNG CHUNG database:**\\n\\n```\\nDTLX (MASTER) ─────────────────── QLHV (SUBSYSTEM)\\n   Hệ thống chính                    Tách ra cho THẦY/GV\\n   Ban giám đốc, Sales, Admin        Giáo viên quản lý HV\\n        │                                 │\\n        └──────── SHARED MONGODB ────────┘\\n              103.253.21.98:27017\\n```\\n\\n**→ QLHV phải đồng bộ dữ liệu với DTLX luôn luôn.**\\n**→ Khi dev QLHV, phải HIỂU DTLX schema vì cùng DB.**\\n\\n## Project Identity\\n- **DTLX Name**: AHV DTLX (Đào Tạo Lái Xe) — MASTER\\n- **QLHV Name**: AHV QLHV (Quản Lý Học Viên) — SUBSYSTEM\\n- **Telegram\\n\\nSource: memory/dtlx-context.md#L1-L46\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/dtlx-context.md#L1-L46\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"89ccf26b7040ce021e9526b7117935aab4b4418e9afc2e7f38a71f602ec196dd\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/2026-04-14.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 21,\n      \"endLine\": 41,\n      \"score\": 0.7222095086420897,\n      \"textScore\": 0.7222095086420897,\n      \"snippet\": \"3. `/users/sales/counter` → 500: `docCounter[0] || {}` for empty aggregate\\n  4. `/lessons/detail-by-date` → server crash: route reorder (`/:id` catchall moved after specific routes)\\n  5. `/teacher-infos` → 404: added `router.get('/')` route\\n\\n## 08: